<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Upload dan Tampilkan Gambar</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/demis.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="header">
      <div class="logo-pbk">
        <img src="/image/logo-pbk.png" alt="" />
        <h3>Paguyuban <br />Barudak Komputer</h3>
      </div>
      <nav class="navbar">
        <a href="/">Beranda</a>
        <a href="/informasi">Informasi</a>
        <a href="/profil">Profil</a>

        <!-- Dropdown Pengurus -->
        <div class="dropdown">
          <a href="#" class="dropbtn">Pengurus</a>
          <div class="dropdown-content">
            <a href="/bph">BPH</a>
            <a href="/akademis">Akademis</a>
            <a href="/eksternal">Eksternal</a>
            <a href="/internal">Internal</a>
            <a href="/medinfo">Medinfo</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Dropdown Demis -->
        <div class="dropdown">
          <a href="#" class="active">Demis</a>
          <div class="dropdown-content">
            <a href="#">2021</a>
            <a href="#">2022</a>
            <a href="#">2023</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </header>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>Demisioner PBK</h1>
        <p>
          Demisioner Paguyuban Barudak Komputer adalah anggota yang telah menyelesaikan masa jabatannya namun tetap menjadi bagian integral dari organisasi. 
          Meskipun secara administratif tidak lagi aktif, ikatan kekeluargaan dan kontribusi mereka tetap mengalir dalam semangat Paguyuban Barudak Komputer. 
          Status demisioner bukan akhir dari keanggotaan, melainkan bentuk transformasi peran dalam keluarga besar Paguyuban Barudak Komputer.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container my-5 item_01">
      <h1 class="text-center mb-4">
          Periode 2021 - 2022 <br />
      </h1>
    
      <% if (gambar.length > 0) { %>
        <div class="grid-container">
          <% gambar.forEach(item => { %>
            <div class="profile-card">
              <img src="/gambar/<%= item.id %>" alt="Gambar <%= item.nama %>" />
              <p><%= item.nama %></p>
            </div>
          <% }) %>
        </div>
      <% } else { %>
        <p class="text-center">Tidak ada gambar yang diupload.</p>
      <% } %>
    </div>
    

    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <footer>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="#">Beranda</a>
        <a href="#">Informasi</a>
        <a href="#">Profil</a>
        <a href="#">Pengurus</a>
        <a href="#">Demis</a>
      </div>
      <div class="social-media">
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pbk.fkom.uniku/" target="_blank"
          ><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i
        ></a>
        <a href="https://x.com/HariInaka8" target="_blank"
          ><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i
        ></a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/pbkfkom_official/" target=""
          ><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i
        ></a>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@pbkfkomuniku" target=""
          ><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i
        ></a>
        <a href="https://id.linkedin.com/in/pbk-fkom-uniku-219b5b245" target=""
          ><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i
        ></a>
      </div>
      <p>Paguyuban Barudak Kompute &copy; 2025. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
